---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "About Me";
---

<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} description="About Juan Rueda">
  <h1>{pageTitle}</h1>

  <div class="bio-content">
    <p>
      I am a <strong>Senior Software Engineer and Tech Lead</strong> specializing
      in scalable web platforms, frontend architecture, and product-driven development.
      With deep experience across <strong
        >JavaScript, Angular, NestJS, and cloud-native systems</strong
      >, I build high-quality software that balances performance, security, and
      real business impact.
    </p>

    <p>
      Throughout my career, I've had the privilege of leading engineering teams
      and building <strong>fintech and enterprise solutions</strong> that have reached
      significant business milestones. I focus on long-term maintainability over short-term
      hacks, valuing clean architecture and developer experience.
    </p>

    <p>
      Outside of work, I enjoy exploring new technologies, contributing to open
      discussions on software architecture, and constantly refining my craft.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .bio-content {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .bio-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .bio-content h2 {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .bio-content h3 {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .bio-content ul {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .bio-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .disclaimer {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--color-dot);
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }
</style>
